.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, brown, fuchsia, apricot, amber
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, russian, australian, spanish
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-cola, 7up, cola, almond-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: azuremaster, old-henry, vegafina, swisher, bolivar
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, turtle, mouse, rat
1. the egyptian is the person who likes fuchsia
2. the swedish is the owner of the turtle
3. the mexican is the person drinking cola
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes apricot
5. the person who likes brown is the person drinking iced-cola
6. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the rabbit
7. the person who likes amber is the old-henry-smoker
8. the person drinking 7up is in the middle
9. the australian is on the far left
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig
11. the owner of the rats is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker
12. the azuremaster-smoker is the person drinking lemonade
13. the russian is the swisher-smoker
14. the australian is on the left or right of the person who likes azure
15. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    amber	|     azure	|      fuchsia	|     brown	|     apricot	|
| Nationality	|   australian	|    mexican	|    egyptian	|    russian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     guinea-pig	|    rat	|     rabbit	|     mouse	|      turtle	|
| Beverage	|    almond-milk	|     cola	|     7up	|    iced-cola	|      lemonade	|
| Cigar		|   old-henry	|    bolivar	|  vegafina	|    swisher	|   azuremaster	|
